text: Chester Mornay Williams (8 August 1970 â€“ 6 September 2019) was a South African rugby union rugby player. He played as a winger for the Springboks from 1993 to 2000. Williams also played rugby for the Western Province in the Currie Cup. He was born in Paarl, South Africa. Williams died on 6 September 2019 from a heart attack at the age of 49. ==References== ==Other websites== *ESPN Profile Category:1970 births Category:2019 deaths Category:Deaths from myocardial infarction Category:South African rugby union players
